@startuml
title SMS - Sequence Diagram (Giang vien diem danh va nhap diem)

actor "Giang vien" as Teacher
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "Django View" as View
participant "Auth/RBAC" as Auth
participant "AttendanceService" as AttSvc
participant "GradeService" as GradeSvc
participant "GPAService" as GpaSvc
database "SQLite" as DB

Teacher -> UI: Mo chi tiet lop hoc phan
UI -> View: GET /classes/{id}
View -> Auth: Kiem tra role + ownership lop
Auth --> View: Hop le
View -> DB: SELECT enrollments + grades + attendance
DB --> View: Du lieu lop
View --> UI: Render danh sach sinh vien

Teacher -> UI: Submit diem danh theo ngay hoc
UI -> View: POST /classes/{id}/attendance
View -> Auth: Kiem tra role + ownership lop
Auth --> View: Hop le
View -> AttSvc: diemDanhLop(classId, ngayHoc, rows)
AttSvc -> DB: UPSERT attendance per enrollment
DB --> AttSvc: OK
AttSvc --> View: Thanh cong
View --> UI: Thong bao da luu diem danh

Teacher -> UI: Nhap/Sua diem cho 1 sinh vien
UI -> View: POST /grades/input
View -> Auth: Kiem tra role + ownership enrollment
Auth --> View: Hop le
View -> GradeSvc: nhapSuaDiem(enrollmentId, lanHoc, scores)
GradeSvc -> DB: INSERT/UPDATE grade
DB --> GradeSvc: gradeSaved
GradeSvc -> GpaSvc: recalculate(student)
GpaSvc -> DB: SELECT latest grade by course
DB --> GpaSvc: grade dataset
GpaSvc -> DB: UPSERT GPA semester + academic standing
DB --> GpaSvc: OK
GpaSvc --> GradeSvc: gpa + xep_loai
GradeSvc --> View: grade + gpa result
View --> UI: Thong bao cap nhat thanh cong

@enduml
